15:23.406 --> 15:24.889
Some of you are like, I don't even know what that is.

15:25.450 --> 15:25.991
Praise God.

15:28.535 --> 15:36.530
You know, I've heard people that think, well, I've got to pray in Shakespearean mode, oh, thou fatherist in heavenest

15:36.802 --> 15:40.506
You are great, great, and mightiest of all time.

15:40.806 --> 15:43.149
They bestowest upon me the blessings.

15:44.130 --> 15:45.151
What does that even mean?

15:46.433 --> 15:48.235
What God wants to hear is your heart.

15:49.316 --> 15:50.017
Lord, here I am.

15:51.639 --> 15:57.005
Lord, this day stunk.

15:57.025 --> 15:58.967
Lord, I'm so frustrated right now.

15:59.848 --> 16:01.410
