16:16.638 --> 16:17.699
That's what he desires.

16:18.981 --> 16:23.266
There's not some big fancy lingo that we've got to establish and bring together.

16:23.466 --> 16:30.674
But come to him, step into his presence, full of belief, confidence,

16:31.778 --> 16:47.073
You're presentable inside and out, again, not because of who you are, but you're forgiven because of Christ and what he's did, holding onto the promises that he's already given understanding and trusting that he is true to his word.

16:48.054 --> 16:50.577
Did you know the Bible says that all of God's promises?

16:52.198 --> 16:56.222
Come on, all of God's promises are yes and amen.

16:58.604 --> 17:00.146
That word amen means so be it.

17:02.626 --> 17:04.308
All of God's promises.

17:05.550 --> 17:06.351
What are promises?

17:06.471 --> 17:09.715
Well, one is, He said, I'll never leave you, I'll never forsake you.

17:12.659 --> 17:14.641
By His stripes we are healed.

17:16.324 --> 17:19.388
That if we confess our sins, He'll forgive us and make us brand new.

17:21.270 --> 17:27.017
So many promises of God that you and I get to hold on to as His followers.

17:28.519 --> 17:30.642
Yet too many times what do we do?

17:30.818 --> 17:34.322
We push those back and we think to ourselves, it's not for me.

17:34.362 --> 17:37.426
I'm not worthy of that.

17:40.250 --> 17:40.891
Listen carefully.

17:42.413 --> 17:43.033
None of us are.

17:44.595 --> 17:45.537
That's why it's grace.

17:47.339 --> 17:47.679
Come on.

17:49.942 --> 17:50.483
That's good.

17:50.543 --> 17:52.946
That's why it's grace.

17:53.410 --> 18:05.924
unmerited favor, not something that we've earned, not something that we deserve, but freely given by God a relationship for you and for me.

18:06.224 --> 18:11.390
Jesus holds in his hand the access that we have to the Father.

18:12.931 --> 18:13.452
All right, let's go.

18:14.293 --> 18:15.874
Four truths that I want to give you tonight.

18:15.894 --> 18:17.176
We've got the digital outlines.

18:17.196 --> 18:18.317
We've got the paper outlines.

18:18.597 --> 18:19.278
Take good notes.

18:19.338 --> 18:20.159
Number one is this.

18:20.500 --> 18:22.802
Prayer is not an obligation.

18:22.978 --> 18:24.220
It's an invitation.

18:25.543 --> 18:28.067
Prayer is not an obligation.

18:29.229 --> 18:30.171
It's an invitation.

18:30.311 --> 18:35.020
Sometimes we feel guilty because we haven't spent time in prayer.

18:35.581 --> 18:40.209
Can I just tell you that guilt is not from God, that guilt is self-inflicted?

18:42.593 --> 18:44.076
Come on.

18:44.256 --> 18:45.138
That's good.

18:45.954 --> 18:47.036
It's self-inflicted.

18:47.096 --> 18:50.240
