19:22.162 --> 19:25.806
Or maybe you get to a restaurant and the line is out the door.

19:25.846 --> 19:30.451
People waiting to be seated and you think, I hope that I get a seat tonight.

19:31.272 --> 19:32.294
We've all been there.

19:32.334 --> 19:39.442
The problem is we equate that to our conversations with God and we think, I hope I'm allowed in.

19:40.034 --> 19:41.937
I hope I'm good enough.

19:42.257 --> 19:44.120
I hope I've earned my way.

19:44.360 --> 19:48.926
But the Bible doesn't say anything about earning our way or being good enough.

19:49.687 --> 19:52.351
It's as we can enter in.

19:52.371 --> 19:55.075
Here's what we've got to understand.

19:55.135 --> 19:57.137
Prayer is not about fulfilling a duty.

