Because of Jesus, because of his sacrifice, because of the price that he paid, because he rose from the grave, the curtain, the veil, into the most holy place was torn.

21:23.778 --> 21:26.580
The gospels tell us all about this.

21:26.861 --> 21:28.242
Matthew, Mark, Luke, and John.

21:28.866 --> 21:32.070
